data.description: Discover your dream family home nestled in the peaceful rural area of West Palm Beach, Florida. This charming single-family residence offers the perfect blend of country living and modern convenience, with four spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Set on a sprawling 1.25-acre lot, you'll have plenty of room to spread out and enjoy the tranquility of your surroundings. Imagine weekends spent lounging by the large pool or entertaining friends on the open porch and balcony. The backyard offers a lush oasis, complete with a sprinkler system and a securely fenced area designated for RV parking. When you need to venture out, you're just 10 minutes away from cinemas, pharmacies, banks, shopping centers, schools, and the library.
